==Description== <!--T:2-->

<!--T:3-->
The {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_MergeCells.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_MergeCells|Spreadsheet MergeCells]]}} tool merges at least two selected cells in an existing spreadsheet in the active document.

==Usage== <!--T:4-->

<!--T:5-->
# Make sure there is an active {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_CreateSheet.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_CreateSheet|Spreadsheet]]}} open so that the button is enabled.
# Select at least two contiguous cells.
# Press the {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_MergeCells.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_MergeCells|Spreadsheet MergeCells]]}} button.


